These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, martial-arts, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, folk, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, british, american, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, skateboard, helicopter, scooter
1. the british is the fan of pop##1
2. the american is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the british is the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the mexican is on the far right##1
9. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific   | superhero  | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | pop    | electronic      | folk    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | british | american | mexican |
| Transport     | scooter  | van       | skateboard    | helicopter     |

