.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, reading, chess, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, family, martial-arts, animation
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, guinea-pig, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, parkour, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the rat is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's sport is basketball##2
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching animation movies and the owner of the rat##2
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | reading    | chess  | collecting    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster      | family  | animation  | martial-arts |
| Pet           | rat      | guinea-pig       | hamster      | chinchilla       |
| Sport         | cricket    | volleyball | parkour | basketball |

