.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, strawberry, pomegranate, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking, collecting, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, mechanic, manager, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, bus, trike
1. the manager is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
8. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
9. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person eating pomegranate and the mechanic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | strawberry | pomegranate     | zucchini   | apple     |
| Hobby       | filmmaking   | magic-tricks   | collecting | drawing |
| Job         | police-officer   | manager | project-manager       | mechanic    |
| Transport   | bus    | snowmobile | quad-bike  | trike    |

