.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, software-developer, analyst, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, animation, mystery
4 different pets are kept: snake, dog, turtle, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, golf, cricket
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the dancer##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the dog##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is the analyst##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the software-developer is between the owner of the snake and the social-worker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | dancer  | social-worker | software-developer     | analyst |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | adventure  | animation | horror       |
| Pet           | dog       | fish    | turtle      | snake           |
| Sport         | skiing | sailing   | cricket   | golf         |

