 3. the videographer is the person eating papaya##1
 4. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the photographer is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the teacher is the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person eating pepper is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching action movies##2
10. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
