6. the british is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the british is on the left of the software-developer##1
8. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
9. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
