3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the taxi and the person watching superhero movies##2
6. the person drinking 7up is the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
