 6. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
 7. the librarian is on the left of the electrician##1
 8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
 9. the journalist is between the paramedic and the person who's sport is swimming##2
10. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
