.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, iced-tea, water
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, orange, grapes, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, camping, fishing, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, snake, rabbit
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating grapes##2
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | iced-tea    | water      | soy-milk |
| Food       | grapefruit        | peas       | grapes       | orange     |
| Hobby      | fishing | traveling | magic-tricks | camping        |
| Pet        | guinea-pig       | rabbit     | snake         | mouse           |

