 3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 5. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the turtle##2
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating eggplant##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
